Pepper 16

&lt;b&gt;On what operating system?&lt;/b&gt;
Windows 7

&lt;b&gt;What browser are you using?&lt;/b&gt;
17.0.942.0 dev-m

&lt;b&gt;What steps will reproduce the problem?&lt;/b&gt;
1. Download and compile https://code.google.com/p/field-of-uniforms-and-drawcalls/source/checkout
2. Run the program , and press F to enter full screen mode
3. Move the mouse (without clicking) and notice how smooth it is
4. Click the mouse (which captures it) and notice how slow the mouse movement becomes.

&lt;b&gt;What is the expected output?&lt;/b&gt;
Mouse movement with capture shouldn't be slow.

&lt;b&gt;What do you see instead?&lt;/b&gt;
Mouse movement sampling in fullscreen w/ mouselock is slower than non mouselock.



